Source: pghydro
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/pghydro/pghydro

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pghydro
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pghydro
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION, postgresql-PGVERSION-postgis-3
Description: Drainage network analysis extensions for PostgreSQL and PostGIS
 PgHydro is a SQL-only bundle of PostgreSQL and PostGIS extensions for
 drainage network analysis and water-resources decision support. This package
 installs pghydro, pgh_raster, pgh_hgm, pgh_output, pgh_output_en_au,
 pgh_output_pt_br, and pgh_consistency.
